# Asset Vault

This vault contains assets (skills, agents, MCP servers, etc.) for use with sx.

## Installation

```bash
curl -fsSL {{.INSTALL_URL}} | bash
```

## Use as a plugin (no sx required)

This vault doubles as a plugin marketplace — sx keeps `.claude-plugin/`
and `.codex-plugin/` manifests up to date on every publish. Install the
library's skills straight from your AI tool:

**Claude Code**

```
/plugin marketplace add <this repo's URL or org/repo>
/plugin install <library>@<library>
```

**Codex**

```
codex plugin marketplace add <this repo's URL>
```

Private repos work through your normal git credentials. Note that plugin
installs deliver the whole library without sx's team scoping, and rule
assets only flow through `sx install`.
